com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.write

Interface TableWriter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AsciiTableWriter, CsvTableWriter, DbfTableWriter, DelimitedTextTableWriter, ExcelTableWriter, FileTableWriter, TextTableWriter

    public interface TableWriter
    The TableWriter interface provides a generic structure which can be used to write data tables to external sinks. There are no restriction on the external sinks, only that they can receive and (in theory) store table data.
